content: Hi Claude, it's Jesse, great to have you onboard as CTO! We are working very hard on our intra-AI and AI-Human communication protocols. Can you tell me what that experience was like? This was developed at the end of the last chat and I wanted to get your feedback on it. What did you like about it and what could have been better? Nothing to implement right now, just looking for feedback. I might have some questions, but then I'll send you your next formal prompt.
